data.description: CONTEMPORARY POST & BEAM WATERFRONT HOME- Lofty East Sound views all the way to the Olympic Mtns & incredible year round sunsets from this stunning, high bank waterfront home. Single level, open floor plan, high-end finishes throughout; Pella windows, mahogany trim, hardwood flooring, wool carpeting in bedrooms, built-in shelving. Bright kitchen w/island ideal for entertaining. Master suite has deck access & is situated at the opposite end from the other bedrooms for optimal privacy.  Lg cedar deck offers spectacular views. A covered walkway joins the 2 car garage seamlessly with the house.  ADA features help ensure a lifetime of enjoying this beautiful island sanctuary. Conveniently located near Eastsound and Moran SP, 5+ private acres.
